1555
01:57:19,223 --> 01:57:25,090
Mr. President, I know this is a topic of yours with the thermoplastic painting.

1556
01:57:25,931 --> 01:57:29,274
During this year's MMA show, I went there.

1557
01:57:29,314 --> 01:57:34,140
I had an opportunity to meet with the company that does the thermoplastic painting.

1558
01:57:34,757 --> 01:57:40,059
and I met with some other city officials who have done the thermoplastic painting.

1559
01:57:41,140 --> 01:57:59,167
Not on all the lines or anything, but they have at least done the crosswalks at different schools and different places, and they said that the thermoplastic lasts five to six years, and it's been a win for them, and I'd like to see us do that again this year.

1560
01:57:59,407 --> 01:58:01,488
I know you've championed this for many years,

1561
01:58:01,915 --> 01:58:04,176
But again, I think it's something that it should be done.

1562
01:58:04,516 --> 01:58:08,437
The company even said they would come down here and do one for free to show us how it would work.

1563
01:58:08,978 --> 01:58:10,298
And I think we should take them up on it.

1564
01:58:11,238 --> 01:58:14,740
And I say at least they do the crosswalks at the schools and different things like that.

1565
01:58:14,760 --> 01:58:16,260
You don't have to do the whole city with them.

1566
01:58:17,681 --> 01:58:18,981
And I would like to amend that.

1567
01:58:22,483 --> 01:58:26,064
As amended on the motion, if I just could add, Councilor.

1568
01:58:26,606 --> 01:58:28,047
President Caviello is absolutely correct.

1569
01:58:28,067 --> 01:58:39,274
The thermoplastic crosswalks are highly reflective, they're slip resistant, they have a life expectancy of four to five years, and they're cost effective in the long run.

1570
01:58:39,374 --> 01:58:39,575
You know.

1571
01:58:39,595 --> 01:58:40,575
Bill O'Reilly said six years.

1572
01:58:40,615 --> 01:58:41,356
They've gotten out of this.

1573
01:58:41,376 --> 01:58:41,816
Six years.

1574
01:58:42,657 --> 01:58:45,999
The state uses them for the state highway and many of their projects.

1575
01:58:46,459 --> 01:58:52,183
So it's a very effective and efficient way of laying down a painted crosswalk.

1576
01:58:52,557 --> 01:58:54,559
without the upkeep year to year of repainting.

