1878
02:24:15,490 --> 02:24:16,350
I can't wait a year.

1879
02:24:16,811 --> 02:24:20,112
I can't wait six months for a consultant to come in and go, wow, are you crazy?

1880
02:24:20,172 --> 02:24:31,918
