02:29:54,426 --> 02:29:56,207
Name and address of the record, please.

1953
02:29:56,227 --> 02:29:59,668
Gene Nuzzo, 35 Parris Street, right around the corner from Salem Street.

1954
02:29:59,828 --> 02:30:03,289
