1958
02:30:17,238 --> 02:30:20,800
With all respect, I'm disinterested in what the mayor's opinion is.

1959
02:30:21,320 --> 02:30:24,162
I'm disinterested in what the community development's opinion is.

1960
02:30:24,763 --> 02:30:27,985
