1968
02:30:54,915 --> 02:30:56,596
It's sewer systems.

1969
02:30:56,696 --> 02:30:57,997
It's backing up the streets.

1970
02:30:58,197 --> 02:31:10,123
It's the fact that when you drive down the streets in our neighborhood, people are cutting through because they're trying to avoid 93 and with the fast 14, the entire state has learned how to cut through the city of Medford.

1971
02:31:10,723 --> 02:31:20,988
So, I mean, I think that we can't handle the additional volume that we're hearing someone somewhere is envisioning in this neighborhood.

1972
02:31:21,028 --> 02:31:22,289
