1976
02:31:40,483 --> 02:31:51,131
So I don't think that having a vision of putting 15, 20 of these down Stalem Street is really gonna do anybody any favor.

1977
02:31:51,831 --> 02:32:01,161
I think we're going to get into a situation where the people who live in the neighbourhood, their properties are going to be devalued because they're not going to be these new buildings.

1978
02:32:01,721 --> 02:32:07,527
