1992
02:33:15,300 --> 02:33:17,142
I don't want it to be a developer's decision.

1993
02:33:17,402 --> 02:33:27,991
So I know it's a little bit strong, my commentary, but I feel like our neighborhood is really on the chopping block very quickly.

1994
02:33:28,582 --> 02:33:31,805
and it will go like dominoes if we don't do something about it.

1995
02:33:31,845 --> 02:33:40,191
