2006
02:34:28,330 --> 02:34:30,792
She did mention that they are due for reassessment.

2007
02:34:30,832 --> 02:34:38,098
So I ask that we look into, rather than a per lateral fee, we look into a charging per fixture.

2008
02:34:38,138 --> 02:34:43,202
I believe our fee amounts are outdated by probably several years.

2009
02:34:43,322 --> 02:34:48,707
