2026
02:36:14,158 --> 02:36:17,879
This is just one that I know I read the city of Cambridge is, um,

2027
02:36:18,598 --> 02:36:28,644
ordinance and it's very different than ours and they're capturing a new construction, much more that could go towards our infrastructure needs, especially in those areas that are being developed.

2028
02:36:30,865 --> 02:36:31,246
