02:37:32,808 --> 02:37:33,688
Councilor Langlois-Carran.

2041
02:37:34,229 --> 02:37:37,451
I think what we do as a city council is make recommendations anyway.

2042
02:37:37,491 --> 02:37:40,794
This is a recommendation that this type of fee be added.

