02:37:40,914 --> 02:37:44,757
I did speak to somebody in the City of Cambridge Engineering Department.

2044
02:37:45,528 --> 02:37:56,116
who did say by charging the per fixture, you do capture more, much more revenue because it's obviously per fixture versus whatever the per lateral is.

2045
02:37:56,136 --> 02:37:58,278
I believe it was just one set fee.

2046
02:37:59,058 --> 02:38:01,540
One, I think it's a hundred dollars, the city of Medford charges.

2047
02:38:01,580 --> 02:38:04,002
